{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://leoshcn.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Return of the Mayflower (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Franklin D. Roosevelt was so impressed by the companion paintings <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Return_of_the_Mayflower\" title=\"Return of the Mayflower\">Return of the Mayflower</a></b></i> <i>(pictured)</i> and <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Surrender_of_the_German_Fleet_to_the_Grand_Fleet_at_Scapa_Flow\" title=\"Surrender of the German Fleet to the Grand Fleet at Scapa Flow\">Surrender of the German Fleet to the Grand Fleet at Scapa Flow</a></b></i> that he commissioned smaller versions for his own private collection?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Return_of_the_Mayflower","retrieved":1773729448819},{"title":"Sol Babitz (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that violinist <b><a href=\"/wiki/Sol_Babitz\" title=\"Sol Babitz\">Sol Babitz</a></b>, a pioneer in <a href=\"/wiki/Historically_informed_performance\" title=\"Historically informed performance\">historically informed performance</a>, was twice evicted by the police from meetings of the American Musicological Society?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sol_Babitz","retrieved":1773729448823},{"title":"green beer (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that some <b><a href=\"/wiki/Green_beer\" title=\"Green beer\">green beer</a></b> is colored with <a href=\"/wiki/Spirulina_(dietary_supplement)\" title=\"Spirulina (dietary supplement)\">spirulina</a> algae?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_beer","retrieved":1773729448825},{"title":"a Canadian skier (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that United States interference almost prevented <b><a href=\"/wiki/Nicolas_Claveau-Laviolette\" title=\"Nicolas Claveau-Laviolette\">a Canadian skier</a></b> from competing for <b><a href=\"/wiki/Venezuela_at_the_2026_Winter_Olympics\" title=\"Venezuela at the 2026 Winter Olympics\">Venezuela at the 2026 Winter Olympics</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicolas_Claveau-Laviolette","retrieved":1773729448827},{"title":"hunt him down in Minecraft (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a YouTuber pays cash bounties for his friends to <b><a href=\"/wiki/Minecraft_Manhunt\" title=\"Minecraft Manhunt\">hunt him down in <i>Minecraft</i></a></b><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minecraft_Manhunt","retrieved":1773729448828},{"title":"Caroline Jones (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Caroline_Jones_(fundraiser)\" title=\"Caroline Jones (fundraiser)\">Caroline Jones</a></b> wore different charity clothes every day in 2015 after her mother died?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caroline_Jones_(fundraiser)","retrieved":1773729448830},{"title":"Old Uncle Ned (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <a href=\"/wiki/Stephen_Foster\" title=\"Stephen Foster\">Stephen Foster</a>'s best-selling song \"<b><a href=\"/wiki/Old_Uncle_Ned\" title=\"Old Uncle Ned\">Old Uncle Ned</a></b>\" made little money for him due to the many pirated publications circulating in the marketplace?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Old_Uncle_Ned","retrieved":1773729448831},{"title":"Pipiet Senja (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the author <b><a href=\"/wiki/Pipiet_Senja\" title=\"Pipiet Senja\">Pipiet Senja</a></b> likened her <a href=\"/wiki/Dawah\" title=\"Dawah\">proselytization</a> through teaching and writing to spreading a virus?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pipiet_Senja","retrieved":1773729448834},{"title":"Mataró (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the locomotive <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Matar%C3%B3_(locomotive)\" title=\"Mataró (locomotive)\">Mataró</a></b></i> was placed on a monument and fell?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matar%C3%B3_(locomotive)","retrieved":1773729448835},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<styl