png 2x\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></span></span></p>\n\t<div class=\"mainpage-shadowbox notheme banner-box-2 banner-box-left\" style=\"width:30%\">\n        <div style=\"position:relative; float:right; margin:-4px;\">\n        <span typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\"><a href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previous_Featured_travel_topics\" title=\"Previous Featured travel topics\"><img alt=\"FTT\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:Writing_Circle_white.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Writing_Circle_white.svg/40px-Writing_Circle_white.svg.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"20\" data-file-type=\"drawing\" height=\"32\" width=\"32\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Writing_Circle_white.svg/60px-Writing_Circle_white.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Writing_Circle_white.svg/120px-Writing_Circle_white.svg.png 2x\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></div>\n\t\t<section data-mw-section-id=\"-1\" id=\"mwLQ\" aria-labelledby=\"Featured_Travel_Topic\"><h2 style=\"font-size:1.25em;\" id=\"Featured_Travel_Topic\" class=\"mw-html-heading\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previous_Featured_travel_topics\" title=\"Previous Featured travel topics\">Featured Travel Topic</a></h2>\n        <section data-mw-section-id=\"-1\" id=\"mwLg\" aria-labelledby=\"Broken_Hill_Xplorer\"><h3 style=\"font-size:2em;\" id=\"Broken_Hill_Xplorer\" class=\"mw-html-heading\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Broken_Hill_Xplorer\" title=\"Broken Hill Xplorer\">Broken Hill Xplorer</a></h3>\n\t\t<div class=\"quote\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Broken_Hill_Xplorer\" title=\"Broken Hill Xplorer\">This once-weekly train offers a great affordable and scenic way to travel across the state of New South Wales, from the state capital of Sydney to the small outback mining town of Broken Hill.</a></div>\n\t</section></section